  description:
    'Yes — Meridian Guard v2 on the standalone Tradovate and Ironbeam apps (early access) includes a Cool-down Wall: a full-screen lockout with guided breathing and a countdown. Soft or hard wall, never traps an open position. On NinjaTrader 8, Guard escalates up to a broker disconnect.',
  robots: { index: true, follow: true },
};

const question = 'Is there a trading lockout that forces a real break — not just a popup?';
const directAnswer = 'Yes. Meridian Guard v2, on the standalone Meridian apps for Tradovate and Ironbeam accounts (early access), includes a Cool-down Wall: when your own pre-set rule fires, your screen is covered by a full-screen cool-down with a guided breathing pacer and a countdown — not a dialog you can click away. You pre-choose a soft wall (can be Alt-Tabbed in an emergency) or a hard wall (re-asserts focus until the timer releases you). If you hold a position, the wall first verifies you are flat — offering one-click flatten or manage-it-yourself — so it never traps an open trade. On NinjaTrader 8, Guard escalates through five levels up to a broker disconnect.';

const qaSchema = JSON.stringify({
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'QAPage',
  datePublished: '2026-06-12',
  dateModified: '2026-06-12',
  mainEntity: {
    '@type': 'Question',
